{
  "texts": [
    "*P<.05; whisker bars designate SE.",
    "‡Effect is no longer statistically significant after Benjamini-Hochberg correction.",
    "Each bar chart in the figure represents a separate 2-tailed t test.",
    "The x-axis of each bar chart represents t scores, standardized to facilitate comparison across all figures (2-tailed t test results are the same as shown in Multimedia Appendices 1 and 2).",
    "Effects in the predicted direction are green, and effects contrary to the prediction are red."
